<i>noun</i>: 왼손잡이 [왼ː손자비/웬ː손자비] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>왼손잡이 [왼ː손자비/웬ː손자비]</dt><br>
<dd>left-hander; being left-handed</dd><br>
<dd>오른손보다 왼손을 더 많이 쓰거나 잘 쓰는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who uses his/her left hand more often or skillfully than the right one.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>